casebody.data:
The FALLS CHURCH, aka The Church at the Falls-The Falls Church, petitioner,
v.
The PROTESTANT EPISCOPAL CHURCH IN THE UNITED STATES of America, et al. No. 13-449. Supreme Court of the United States March 10, 2014.

Case below, 285 Va. 651, 740 S.E.2d 530.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Virginia denied.
